<% content_for :title, "Banuba 検証" %>

<div class="container py-4 banuba-page">
  <div class="row g-4">
    <div class="col-12">
      <div class="card banuba-card" data-bs-theme="light">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h1 class="h4 mb-3">Banuba Web SDK 検証</h1>

          <p class="text-body-secondary mb-3">
            development 限定の検証ページです。Rails 上で Banuba が起動し、
            カメラ映像と effect が適用できるかを確認します。
          </p>

          <div class="small text-body-secondary">
            <div>SDK: <code><%= @banuba_sdk_base_url %></code></div>
            <div>Face tracker: <code><%= @banuba_face_tracker_url %></code></div>
            <div>Effect: <code><%= @banuba_effect_url %></code></div>
          </div>

          <% if @banuba_client_token.blank? %>
            <div class="alert alert-danger mt-3 mb-0" role="alert">
              BANUBA_CLIENT_TOKEN が未設定です。.env を確認してください。
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-12 col-xl-8">
      <div
        class="card banuba-card h-100"
        data-bs-theme="light"
        data-controller="banuba-verification"
        data-banuba-verification-client-token-value="<%= @banuba_client_token %>"
        data-banuba-verification-sdk-base-url-value="<%= @banuba_sdk_base_url %>"
        data-banuba-verification-face-tracker-url-value="<%= @banuba_face_tracker_url %>"
        data-banuba-verification-effect-url-value="<%= @banuba_effect_url %>"
        data-banuba-verification-effect-name-value="<%= @banuba_effect_name %>"
      >
        <div class="card-header d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
          <span>プレビュー</span>
          <span class="badge text-bg-secondary" data-banuba-verification-target="state">idle</span>
        </div>

        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="banuba-preview-wrap">
            <div class="banuba-preview-surface" data-banuba-verification-target="surface"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="banuba-error mt-3" data-banuba-verification-target="error"></div>

          <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3">
            <button
              type="button"
              class="btn btn-primary"
              data-action="banuba-verification#start"
              data-banuba-verification-target="startBtn">
              起動
            </button>

            <button
              type="button"
              class="btn btn-outline-secondary d-none"
              data-action="banuba-verification#stop"
              data-banuba-verification-target="stopBtn">
              停止
            </button>

            <button
              type="button"
              class="btn btn-outline-primary d-none"
              data-action="banuba-verification#reapplyEffect"
              data-banuba-verification-target="effectBtn">
              effect 再適用
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-12 col-xl-4">
      <div class="card banuba-card h-100" data-bs-theme="light">
        <div class="card-header">確認メモ</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="mb-3">
            <div class="fw-semibold">起動時に確認すること</div>
            <ul class="mb-0">
              <li>カメラ権限が取れる</li>
              <li>映像が表示される</li>
              <li>effect 適用で見た目が変わる</li>
              <li>顔移動に追従する</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-3">
            <div class="fw-semibold">安定性</div>
            <ul class="mb-0">
              <li>数分放置で console error が出ない</li>
              <li>停止 → 起動 を数回繰り返して壊れない</li>
              <li>Turbo 遷移後にカメラが残らない</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-0">
            <div class="fw-semibold">URL</div>
            <code><%= dev_banuba_verification_path %></code>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
